    LAM_avg - KAM_avg AS diff_LAM_KAM,
    KAM_avg - SME_avg AS diff_KAM_SME
FROM (
    SELECT 
        MAX(CASE WHEN Segment = 'SME' THEN min_val END) AS SME_avg,
        MAX(CASE WHEN Segment = 'LAM' THEN min_val END) AS LAM_avg,
        MAX(CASE WHEN Segment = 'KAM' THEN min_val END) AS KAM_avg
